Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,THE OTHER HERO
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.05,0:02:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron Berku overwhelmed Mystban!\NAnd yet his blade...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.39,0:02:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...doesn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.72,0:02:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Zaboera?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.81,0:02:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The body of this Superior Being Zombie\Nabsorbs impacts!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No weapon can cut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's truly invincible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.70,0:02:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My brain is a terrifying thing indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.61,0:02:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It truly is the mind of a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.49,0:02:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Never fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We have the Superior Beings'\Nweakness on our side!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.33,0:02:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.54,0:02:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Master, I mean, Mr. Beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him a taste of your Refractor Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.18,0:02:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The Refractor Fist doesn't work on Zombies\Nbecause they're already dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.27,0:02:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember this, rat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called an "upgrade" because\Nit's overcome all previous issues!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:03:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The idea for this Superior Being Zombie\Ncame from that attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If it has a weakness,\Nit would be cutting off my Magic Power...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but I just hide myself\Ndeep inside like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and its weakness disappears!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, use magic attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Howl, Inferno!{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Such pitiful attacks won't work on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That old weasel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Cornering him finally\Nmade him reveal his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All that remains...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dammit!\NNot even my Great Axe has any effect!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with all those spells\Nand weapons stuck in it, it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.92,0:04:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Futile, futile!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron Berku couldn't cut it!\NThere's no way you humans can!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-Dammit!\N-Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, he's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No attack will work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even my force and speed worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing we can do here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.65,0:05:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If we had an ultimate weapon\Nthat used more force and speed,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,then maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean like the Sword of Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get rid of\Nthat annoying Magic Circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Your majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.43,0:05:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one\Nwho can fight you hand to hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How small! How weak! How persistent!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose this is what\NI used to look like to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels magnificent to be a giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Beast King Commandos, attack!\NRescue Mr. Crocodine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:06:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't just wish for what we don't have!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Defeating him and protecting\Nthe Magic Circle is our task!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's the time for us to unite
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and unleash a power\Nthat rivals Dai's own!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's theoretically impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, you don't have a weapon\Nthat can defeat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.02,0:06:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A weapon that can defeat him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A weapon...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We do!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We have... my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Your... life?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think you can win\Nby risking your life, you'll die in vain!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not just risking my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm using it as a weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My life itself can be powerful weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Swords won't work on that monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Nova!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.44,0:07:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I will use all of my life power!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's like his sword is draining his life!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At this rate...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Nova! Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A Life Blade?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll cut him with his!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can expose Zaboera even a little bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,it should be possible to defeat him\Nand stop the Superior Being Zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Don't do it, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I acknowledge your bravery...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:08:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't let you use an attack\Nthat has no hope of succeeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sadly, I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with that Life Blade,\Nthe damage you inflict will be minimal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The power to cut it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and expose Zaboera is beyond you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Now stop that blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, it'll drain\Nall your life energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I never assumed I could win with one blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But a Life Blade cannot be broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hit him again and again\Nand again until I fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.17,0:08:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can leave even a single scratch,\Nthen that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's dying in vain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:08:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not in vain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I die, it will leave something\Nfor everyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I once called myself a Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A Hero?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Nova?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There's... There's such\Na difference in our power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet I was so full of myself,\Ntrying to compete with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the real Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was just jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, difference in strength\Ndoesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:10:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't make sense if\Nonly the strongest person could be a Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what sort of person is a real Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.12,0:10:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it! Sorry! That was too difficult!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's not about\Nwho's stronger or braver.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody calls me the Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But back in your home of Ringaia,\Nyou're the Hero of the North, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then isn't that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.53,0:10:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're helping save people,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,then I'm a Hero and you're a Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We're both Heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you, Dai.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You've giving me confidence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And a new spirit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.92,0:11:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's it! This is...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when I realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,a true Hero is more about\Ninspiring courage than just being brave!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I should die...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,if I can leave even a scratch...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and inspire the others\Nthat remain to attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I may not be a good as Dai...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can still serve as a Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nova... You used to be so selfish.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look at how you've grown!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Your majesty! I leave the rest to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Give the call!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.09,0:11:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,"Everyone, follow that attack!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.10,0:11:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Nova!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.14,0:11:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Nova!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.04,0:12:10.54,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}NORTHERN GRAND BLADE{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:15.54,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}DARK INCENSE{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough. You can relax, Nova.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why go so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Until now, I looked down on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You impressed me, and at the same time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't let you die in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Our blood may be of different colors,\Nbut we value life the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron Berku!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If a life must be spent,\Nit might as well be mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:12:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've lived at least\Nten times as long as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had the sort of resolve you did...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I could have defeated that enemy easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I summon you! The ultimate weapon\NI've dedicated my life to!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A new enemy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand back! It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the ultimate superweapon?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what kind of weapon\Nyou bring out now,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,it won't work on\Nmy Superior Being Zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pulverize that little rock\Nbefore you can use it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! My blades?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside that hunk of stone,\Nthere is something incredibly powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. You're a real help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved me the trouble of opening it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Swords?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.35,0:14:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Two of them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I call them...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The Star Emperor Swords!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The Star Emperor Swords?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So these two swords\Nare his ultimate weapon?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The Star Emperor Swords?!\NWhat a pretentious name!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the ultimate weapon\Nthat I've spent over a century creating.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:15:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only weapon in the world\Nmade exclusively for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dual-wielding?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What intensity!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But will it work on\Nthe Superior Being Zombie?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It just looks like\Na clumsy pair of swords!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If it's swords, then it doesn't matter\Nhow hard they are!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing to fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.42,0:15:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I see, Ron Berku!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:16:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You boast about those swords,\Nbut you're unsure of their strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're scared, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}H-He...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, I am scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Not because they might be weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But because\Nthey are overwhelmingly powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I will swing these swords only once!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Right and left! Once strike apiece!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When I do, even I won't be left unscathed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm making certain my attack\Ncan hit you and cut you into four!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the most powerful\NRon Berku Style sword skill...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.80,0:17:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}The Star Emperor Cross Slash!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Look! It was as I expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing! Not a single...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You can brag in the afterlife...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,about that parting cross slash I gave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.39,0:18:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.45,0:18:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron Berku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to his arms?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks painful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.55,0:18:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"Again"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.13,0:18:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,When I use the Star Emperor Cross Slash...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,it shatters both the swords and my arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Nearly 200 years ago,\NI lost the use of my arms the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.53,0:18:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The Star Emperor Cross Slash\Nis too powerful an attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.99,0:19:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment I tried it,\Nit ruined my arms and swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you just saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}More than my own strength,\NI cursed the weakness of my weapons.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I became a weaponsmith to create\Nweapons I could use at full strength.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was the Star Emperor Swords.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it's an incomplete prototype.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have completed it sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.22,0:19:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I forged the Sword of Dai,\NI've been focused on helping his party.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.36,0:19:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The reason I worked so hard\Non the Sword of Dai...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}was likely because I knew the frustration\Nof being too strong to wield a weapon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.33,0:19:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you've been holding back\Nyour strength until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if you hadn't\Nyou would only destroy yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,for me... for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,you used an incomplete superweapon,\Nknowing what it would do to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better than having\Na young man like you die in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.39,0:20:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My one regret...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.94,0:20:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is that I won't be able\Nto make weapons for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.15,0:20:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My arms won't heal for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably not in your lifetimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... Then use my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.21,0:20:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the day your wounds have recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I will complete\Nyour shattered Star Emperor Swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nova!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not just strong.\NYou're worthy of respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If you will let me,\NI wish to learn from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.57,0:21:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, for starters...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you open my bottle for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nova, you've finally found them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Someone you can call Master\Nand a path to walk on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.29,0:21:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.26,0:21:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear. I guess I should start\Nby teaching you how to open a bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.33,0:22:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}C-Crocodine?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.18,0:22:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, where are you going all alone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.18,0:22:17.81,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nee hitoridake de doko e yukuno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.69,0:22:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I gaze at you from behind\Nas you begin to walk away{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.69,0:22:28.36,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}arukidasu kimi no ushirosugata wo nagameru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.37,0:22:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, where are you going all alone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.37,0:22:36.16,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nee hitoridake de doko e yukuno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.96,0:22:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We act tough and follow our hearts{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.96,0:22:45.38,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}massugu de tsuyogari na sonna bokura ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.55,0:22:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And we began this tale together{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.55,0:22:49.80,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hajimeta monogatari{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.30,0:22:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Beyond the horizon something glimmers{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.30,0:22:56.10,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}chiheisen no mukou de kirameiteiru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.27,0:23:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've been seeking something certain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.27,0:23:02.48,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tashika na mono sagashitsuzukete iruno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.11,0:23:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the distant sky, dancing in the wind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.11,0:23:09.32,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}haruka sora ni kaze ni nori matte{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.49,0:23:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The birds sing as though\Nilluminating the future{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.49,0:23:15.12,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tobu tori wa naiteita mirai wo terasuyouni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.29,0:23:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promise that connects us\NThe adventure we share{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.29,0:23:20.92,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wo tsunagu yakusoku to\Nbokura de tsumugu bouken wo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.08,0:23:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Again in this world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.08,0:23:27.09,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mata kono sekai de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.05,0:23:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ron Berku cut down Zaboera's\NSuperior Being Zombie,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.27,0:23:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the battle of Loroi Valley\Nended in victory.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.35,0:23:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meanwhile, in Ban Palace, Hyunckel\Nfights a horde of Underworld monsters.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.19,0:23:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eventually, one person appears,\Nmowing down the monsters.{\i0}
